{"title":"manufacturing - Raven","url":"https://sysmayal.ngrok.io/raven/AMB-Wellness/AMB-Wellness-manufacturing","summary":"This is the manufacturing channel in Raven (an ERPNext-integrated system). The channel shows conversations between team members and a bot named sales_order_bot. The bot handles various manufacturing operations including IoT sensor readings, work orders, BOM management, and sales-purchase cycles. A critical error was observed: the bot repeatedly returned 'Error: name is_confirm is not defined' when trying to create IoT sensor readings without the '!' prefix. After using the forced execution syntax '!create', the bot worked correctly. The bot displays confidence levels (HIGH/UNCERTAIN) and autonomy levels (LEVEL 1/2) for each response. The help command reveals extensive capabilities for manufacturing workflows, sales order follow-up, R&D operations, BOM creation, and document management.","key_points":["Bot name: sales_order_bot - handles ERPNext operations for manufacturing, sales, and purchasing","Error encountered: 'Error: name is_confirm is not defined' - occurs when using @ai create command without confirmation","Error resolution: Using '!create' (force execute) prefix bypasses the is_confirm error","Successful IoT sensor reading created for sensor rpi-iot-l01 with temperature 30.0°C and humidity 55%","Bot displays confidence levels: CONFIDENCE: HIGH or UNCERTAIN","Bot displays autonomy levels: AUTONOMY: LEVEL 1 or LEVEL 2","Manufacturing workflow supported: Work Order → Submit → Issue Materials → Job Cards → Complete → FG Entry","Available bots: @ai (general), @sales_order_follow_up, @rnd_bot, @bom_creator","Key manufacturing commands: show work orders, create work order, submit work order, issue materials, finish work order","Sales-purchase cycle commands: opportunities, material requests, RFQs, supplier quotations, purchase orders, delivery notes","Members in channel: Luis Pedroza Duarte, Estefania Loera, Alvaro Ceniceros Del Río, Administrator Technical, Alan, Alicia Medina, Daniel Flores"],"relevant_links":["https://sysmayal.ngrok.io/raven/AMB-Wellness/AMB-Wellness-amb-general","https://sysmayal.ngrok.io/raven/AMB-Wellness/AMB-Wellness-shipping","https://sysmayal.ngrok.io/raven/AMB-Wellness/AMB-Wellness-quality-inspector","https://sysmayal.ngrok.io/raven/AMB-Wellness/AMB-Wellness-quality","https://sysmayal.ngrok.io/raven/AMB-Wellness/AMB-Wellness-maintenance-amb-w"],"file_name":"raven_manufacturing_channel_messages.json"}
